+### **Fuzzy Matching Guidelines:**
+
+**Exact Matches:**
+- Direct value matches: "123456789012" → {{AWS_ACCOUNT_ID}}
+- In JSON: {"account_id": "123456789012"} → {"account_id": "{{AWS_ACCOUNT_ID}}"}
